snippet.title: Zack Freedman
snippet.description:
I'm a cyborg hardware hacker from the near future! I make unnecessarily high-effort videos on YouTube, and disappointingly low-effort streams on Twitch. I was a freelance prototyper, but when the pandemic shut down all the meetups, I turned to YouTube. I hoped to find business, but instead I found ✨FRIENDSHIP✨

Send gizmos, gadgets, and samples to the Voidstar Mailbag!
Voidstar Lab c/o Zack Freedman

Westminster, CO 80031
